nts</p></div><div class=\"rounded-[24px] border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04] px-5 py-5\"><p class=\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-white/42\">Auction timer</p><p class=\"mt-3 font-display text-4xl uppercase text-white\">00:15</p><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-[color:var(--muted-foreground)]\">Backend-driven countdown</p></div><div class=\"rounded-[24px] border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04] px-5 py-5\"><p class=\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-white/42\">Purse board</p><p class=\"mt-3 font-display text-4xl uppercase text-white\">Live</p><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-[color:var(--muted-foreground)]\">Persisted spend tracking</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"mt-10 grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-3\"><div class=\"h-full\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-[30px] border shadow-[inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.08),0_28px_80px_rgba(0,0,0,0.44)] backdrop-blur-2xl before:pointer-events-none before:absolute before:inset-x-0 before:top-0 before:h-px before:bg-gradient-to-r before:from-transparent before:via-white/18 before:to-transparent group h-full border-white/8 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(22,22,24,0.96),rgba(8,8,10,0.98))] transition-[transform,border-color,box-shadow] duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-white/14 hover:shadow-[inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.08),0_30px_90px_rgba(0,0,0,0.4)]\"><div class=\"flex flex-col p-6 sm:p-7 gap-5\"><div class=\"h-px w-14 bg-white/26\"></div><div class=\"flex h-[3.25rem] w-[3.25rem] items-center justify-center rounded-[22px] border border-white/10 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.08),rgba(255,255,255,0.03))] text-white transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-[1.03]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-trophy h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 14.66v1.626a2 2 0 0 1-.976 1.696A5 5 0 0 0 7 21.978\"></path><path d=\"M14 14.66v1.626a2 2 0 0 0 .976 1.696A5 5 0 0 1 17 21.978\"></path><path d=\"M18 9h1.5a1 1 0 0 0 0-5H18\"></path><path d=\"M4 22h16\"></path><path d=\"M6 9a6 6 0 0 0 12 0V3a1 1 0 0 0-1-1H7a1 1 0 0 0-1 1z\"></path><path d=\"M6 9H4.5a1 1 0 0 1 0-5H6\"></path></svg></div><div><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-white/46\">Access</p><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-white mt-4 font-display text-[2rem] uppercase leading-[0.94] tracking-wide sm:text-[2.2rem]\">Private room control</h3></div></div><div class=\"p-6 sm:p-7 sm:pt-0 pt-1\"><p class=\"text-sm leading-7 text-[color:var(--muted-foreground)] sm:text-[15px]\">Create invite-led auction rooms with stable roles, locked franchises, and a clean host-managed flow.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"h-full\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-[30px] border shadow-[inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.08),0_28px_80px_rgba(0,0,0,0.44)] backdrop-blur-2xl before:pointer-events-none before:absolute before:inset-x-0 before:top-0 before:h-px before:bg-gradient-to-r before:from-transparent before:via-white/18 before:to-transparent group h-full border-white/8 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(22,22,24,0.96),rgba(8,8,10,0.98))] transition-[transform,border-color,box-shadow] duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-white/14 hover:shadow-[inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.08),0_30px_90px_rgba(0,0,0,0.4)]\"><div class=\"flex flex-col p-6 sm:p-7 gap-5\"><div class=\"h-px w-14 bg-white/26\"></div><div class=\"flex h-[3.25rem] w-[3.25rem] items-center justify-center rounded-[22px] border border-white/10 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.08),rgba(255,255,255,0.03))] text-white transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-[1.03]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-layout-dashboard h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect width=\"7\" height=\"9\" x=\"3\" y=\"3\" rx=\"1\"></rect><rect width=\"7\" height=\"5\" x=\"14\" y=\"3\" rx=\"1\"></rect><rect width=\"7\" height=\"9\" x=\"14\" y=\"12\" rx=\"1\"></rect><rect width=\"7\" height=\"5\" x=\"3\" y=\"16\" rx=\"1\"></rect></svg></div><div><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-white/46\">Realtime</p><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-white mt-4 font-display text-[2rem] uppercase leading-[0.94] tracking-wide sm:text-[2.2rem]\">Live bidding board</h3></div></div><div class=\"p-6 sm:p-7 sm:pt-0 pt-1\"><p class=\"text-sm leading-7 text-[color:var(--muted-foreground)] sm:text-[15px]\">Current player, bid, timer, and purse movement stay readable at a glance during active rounds.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"h-full\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-[30px] border shadow-[inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.08),0_28px_80px_rgba(0,0,0,0.44)] backdrop-blur-2xl before:pointer-events-none before:absolute before:inset-x-0 before:top-0 before:h-px before:bg-gradient-to-r before:from-transparent before:via-white/18 before:to-transparent group h-full border-white/8 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(22,22,24,0.96),rgba(8,8,10,0.98))] transition-[transform,border-color,box-shadow] duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-white/14 hover:shadow-[inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.08),0_30px_90px_rgba(0,0,0,0.4)]\"><div class=\"flex flex-col p-6 sm:p-7 gap-5\"><div class=\"h-px w-14 bg-white/26\"></div><div class=\"flex h-[3.25rem] w-[3.25rem] items-center justify-center rounded-[22px] border border-white/10 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.08),rgba(255,255,255,0.03))] text-white transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-[1.03]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-radio h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16.247 7.761a6 6 0 0 1 0 8.478\"></path><path d=\"M19.075 4.933a10 10 0 0 1 0 14.134\"></path><path d=\"M4.925 19.067a10 10 0 0 1 0-14.134\"></path><path d=\"M7.753 16.239a6 6 0 0 1 0-8.478\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"2\"></circle></svg></div><div><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-white/46\">Presence</p><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-white mt-4 font-display text-[2rem] uppercase leading-[0.94] tracking-wide sm:text-[2.2rem]\">Multiplayer seat map</h3></div></div><div class=\"p-6 sm:p-7 sm:pt-0 pt-1\"><p class=\"text-sm leading-7 text-[color:var(--muted-foreground)] sm:text-[15px]\">Hosts, participants, and viewers enter the same room state and stay synchronized across refreshes and reconnects.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"h-full\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-[30px] border shadow-[inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.08),0_28px_80px_rgba(0,0,0,0.44)] backdrop-blur-2xl before:pointer-events-none before:absolute before:inset-x-0 before:top-0 before:h-px before:bg-gradient-to-r before:from-transparent before:via-white/18 before:to-transparent group h-full border-white/8 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(22,22,24,0.96),rgba(8,8,10,0.98))] transition-[transform,border-color,box-shadow] duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-white/14 hover:shadow-[inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.08),0_30px_90px_rgba(0,0,0,0.4)]\"><div class=\"flex flex-col p-6 sm:p-7 gap-5\"><div class=\"h-px w-14 bg-white/26\"></div><div class=\"flex h-[3.25rem] w-[3.25rem] items-center justify-center rounded-[22px] border border-white/10 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.08),rgba(255,255,255,0.03))] text-white transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-[1.03]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-gavel h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m14 13-8.381 8.38a1 1 0 0 1-3.001-3l8.384-8.381\"></path><path d=\"m16 16 6-6\"></path><path d=\"m21.5 10.5-8-8\"></path><path d=\"m8 8 6-6\"></path><path d=\"m8.5 7.5 8 8\"></path></svg></div><div><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-white/46\">Control</p><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-white mt-4 font-display text-[2rem] uppercase leading-[0.94] tracking-wide sm:text-[2.2rem]\">Auction lifecycle</h3></div></div><div class=\"p-6 sm:p-7 sm:pt-0 pt-1\"><p class=\"text-sm leading-7 text-[color:var(--muted-foreground)] sm:text-[15px]\">Pause, settle, and recover rooms with a backend-driven auction engine instead of local-only browser state.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"h-full\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-[30px] border shadow-[inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.08),0_28px_80px_rgba(0,0,0,0.44)] backdrop-blur-2xl before:pointer-events-none before:absolute before:inset-x-0 before:top-0 before:h-px before:bg-gradient-to-r before:from-transparent before:via-white/18 before:to-transparent group h-full border-white/8 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(22,22,24,0.96),rgba(8,8,10,0.98))] transition-[transform,border-color,box-shadow] duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-white/14 hover:shadow-[inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.08),0_30px_90px_rgba(0,0,0,0.4)]\"><div class=\"flex flex-col p-6 sm:p-7 gap-5\"><div class=\"h-px w-14 bg-white/26\"></div><div class=\"flex h-[3.25rem] w-[3.25rem] items-center justify-center rounded-[22px] border border-white/10 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.08),rgba(255,255,255,0.03))] text-white transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-[1.03]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield-check h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg></div><div><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-white/46\">System</p><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-white mt-4 font-display text-[2rem] uppercase leading-[0.94] tracking-wide sm:text-[2.2rem]\">Typed room system</h3></div></div><div class=\"p-6 sm:p-7 sm:pt-0 pt-1\"><p class=\"text-sm leading-7 text-[color:var(--muted-foreground)] sm:text-[15px]\">Clean shared contracts keep auth, room access, realtime events, and persistence easier to extend safely.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"h-full\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-[30px] border shadow-[inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.08),0_28px_80px_rgba(0,0,0,0.44)] backdrop-blur-2xl before:pointer-events-none before:absolute before:inset-x-0 before:top-0 before:h-px before:bg-gradient-to-r before:from-transparent before:via-white/18 before:to-transparent group h-full border-white/8 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(22,22,24,0.96),rgba(8,8,10,0.98))] transition-[transform,border-color,box-shadow] duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-white/14 hover:shadow-[inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.08),0_30px_90px_rgba(0,0,0,0.4)]\"><div class=\"flex flex-col p-6 sm:p-7 gap-5\"><div class=\"h-px w-14 bg-white/26\"></div><div class=\"flex h-[3.25rem] w-[3.25rem] items-center justify-center rounded-[22px] border border-white/10 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.08),rgba(255,255,255,0.03))] text-white transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-[1.03]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-sparkles h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M11.017 2.814a1 1 0 0 1 1.966 0l1.051 5.558a2 2 0 0 0 1.594 1.594l5.558 1.051a1 1 0 0 1 0 1.966l-5.558 1.051a2 2 0 0 0-1.594 1.594l-1.051 5.558a1 1 0 0 1-1.966 0l-1.051-5.558a2 2 0 0 0-1.594-1.594l-5.558-1.051a1 1 0 0 1 0-1.966l5.558-1.051a2 2 0 0 0 1.594-1.594z\"></path><path d=\"M20 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M22 4h-4\"></path><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"20\" r=\"2\"></circle></svg></div><div><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-white/46\">Polish</p><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-white mt-4 font-display text-[2rem] uppercase leading-[0.94] tracking-wide sm:text-[2.2rem]\">Fast, restrained motion</h3></div></div><div class=\"p-6 sm:p-7 sm:pt-0 pt-1\"><p class=\"text-sm leading-7 text-[color:var(--muted-foreground)] sm:text-[15px]\">Motion is used to clarify live changes, not to decorate the screen during high-pressure bidding moments.</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"pb-14 sm:pb-16\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-full max-w-[1400px] px-5 sm:px-7 lg:px-10\"><div class=\"grid gap-6 xl:grid-cols-[1.04fr_0.96fr]\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-[30px] border shadow-[inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.08),0_28px_80px_rgba(0,0,0,0.44)] backdrop-blur-2xl before:pointer-events-none before:absolute before:inset-x-0 before:top-0 before:h-px before:bg-gradient-to-r before:from-transparent before:via-white/18 before:to-transparent border-white/12 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(20,20,22,0.96),rgba(8,8,10,0.98))]\"><div class=\"p-6 sm:p-8\"><div class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-4\"><div><p class=\"text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.34em] text-white/46\">Auction room layout</p><h2 class=\"mt-4 font-display text-5xl uppercase leading-[0.9] text-white sm:text-6xl\">Critical bidding data stays visible first.</h2></div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-up-right mt-1 h-5 w-5 text-white/55\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M7 7h10v10\"></path><path d=\"M7 17 17 7\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"mt-8 grid gap-4 lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr_0.9fr]\"><div class=\"rounded-[28px] border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04] p-6\"><div class=\"grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-3\"><div class=\"flex min-h-[112px] items-center justify-center rounded-[22px] border border-white/10 bg-black/20 px-4 py-4 text-center\"><p class=\"max-w-[11ch] text-balance font-display text-[1.6rem] uppercase leading-[0.94] text-white sm:text-[1.82rem]\">Player card</p></div><div class=\"flex min-h-[112px] items-center justify-center rounded-[22px] border border-white/10 bg-black/20 px-4 py-4 text-center\"><p class=\"max-w-[11ch] text-balance font-display text-[1.6rem] uppercase leading-[0.94] text-white sm:text-[1.82rem]\">Bid panel</p></div><div class=\"flex min-h-[112px] items-center justify-center rounded-[22px] border border-white/10 bg-black/20 px-4 py-4 text-center\"><p class=\"max-w-[11ch] text-balance font-display text-[1.6rem] uppercase leading-[0.94] text-white sm:text-[1.82rem]\">Team purse board</p></div></div><p class=\"mt-5 max-w-2xl text-sm leading-7 text-[color:var(--muted-foreground)]\">The auction room is optimized for desktop scanning first, with current player, current bid, timer, highest bidder, and team purse movement all visible before the fold.</p></div><div class=\"space-y-3\"><div class=\"rounded-[24px] border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04] px-5 py-5\"><p class=\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-white/42\">Auction Pulse</p><p class=\"mt-3 font-display text-4xl uppercase leading-none text-white\">Live Room</p><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-[color:var(--muted-foreground)]\">Realtime auction state, room membership, and purse movement in one focused workspace.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-[24px] border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04] px-5 py-5\"><p class=\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-white/42\">Host Control</p><p class=\"mt-3 font-display text-4xl uppercase leading-none text-white\">Private</p><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-[color:var(--muted-foreground)]\">Hosts control the room lifecycle while participants only see the actions their role allows.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-[24px] border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04] px-5 py-5\"><p class=\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-white/42\">Player Feed</p><p class=\"mt-3 font-display text-4xl uppercase leading-none text-white\">Randomized</p><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-[color:var(--muted-foreground)]\">Players load from the database into room-specific auction order for each new room.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"grid gap-5\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-[30px] border shadow-[inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.08),0_28px_80px_rgba(0,0,0,0.44)] backdrop-blur-2xl before:pointer-events-none before:absolute before:inset-x-0 before:top-0 before:h-px before:bg-gradient-to-r before:from-transparent before:via-white/18 before:to-transparent border-white/10 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(20,20,22,0.96),rgba(8,8,10,0.98))]\"><div class=\"flex h-full items-start gap-4 p-6 sm:p-7\"><div class=\"flex h-12 w-12 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-[18px] border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield-check h-5 w-5 text-white\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg></div><div><h3 class=\"font-display text-3xl uppercase leading-[0.96] text-white\">Host-controlled pacing</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-[color:var(--muted-foreground)]\">Only the host can start, pause, or settle lots, while the rest of the room stays synchronized.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-[30px] border shadow-[inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.08),0_28px_80px_rgba(0,0,0,0.44)] backdrop-blur-2xl before:pointer-events-none before:absolute before:inset-x-0 before:top-0 before:h-px before:bg-gradient-to-r before:from-transparent before:via-white/18 before:to-transparent border-white/10 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(20,20,22,0.96),rgba(8,8,10,0.98))]\"><div class=\"flex h-full items-start gap-4 p-6 sm:p-7\"><div class=\"flex h-12 w-12 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-[18px] border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-users-round h-5 w-5 text-white\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M18 21a8 8 0 0 0-16 0\"></path><circle cx=\"10\" cy=\"8\" r=\"5\"></circle><path d=\"M22 20c0-3.37-2-6.5-4-8a5 5 0 0 0-.45-8.3\"></path></svg></div><div><h3 class=\"font-display text-3xl uppercase leading-[0.96] text-white\">Role-aware room access</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-[color:var(--muted-foreground)]\">Participants, viewers, and hosts each enter the room with backend-enforced permissions and a stable identity.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-[30px] border shadow-[inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.08),0_28px_80px_rgba(0,0,0,0.44)] backdrop-blur-2xl before:pointer-events-none before:absolute before:inset-x-0 before:top-0 before:h-px before:bg-gradient-to-r before:from-transparent before:via-white/18 before:to-transparent border-white/10 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(20,20,22,0.96),rgba(8,8,10,0.98))]\"><div class=\"flex h-full items-start gap-4 p-6 sm:p-7\"><div class=\"flex h-12 w-12 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-[18px] border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-radio h-5 w-5 text-white\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16.247 7.761a6 6 0 0 1 0 8.478\"></path><path d=\"M19.075 4.933a10 10 0 0 1 0 14.134\"></path><path d=\"M4.925 19.067a10 10 0 0 1 0-14.134\"></path><path d=\"M7.753 16.239a6 6 0 0 1 0-8.478\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"2\"></circle></svg></div><div><h3 class=\"font-display text-3xl uppercase leading-[0.96] text-white\">Realtime state recovery</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-[color:var(--muted-foreground)]\">Room snapshots, bids, purse updates, and completed outcomes rebuild correctly after refresh or reconnect.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"pb-14 sm:pb-16\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-full max-w-[1400px] px-5 sm:px-7 lg:px-10\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-[30px] border shadow-[inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.08),0_28px_80px_rgba(0,0,0,0.44)] backdrop-blur-2xl before:pointer-events-none before:absolute before:inset-x-0 before:top-0 before:h-px before:bg-gradient-to-r before:from-transparent before:via-white/18 before:to-transparent border-white/12 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(24,24,27,0.96),rgba(8,8,10,0.98))]\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-8 p-6 sm:p-8 lg:flex-row lg:items-end lg:justify-between lg:p-10\"><div class=\"max-w-2xl\"><p class=\"text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.34em] text-white/46\">Ready to run</p><h2 class=\"mt-5 font-display text-5xl uppercase leading-[0.9] text-white sm:text-6xl\">Create a private room and start the auction when the table is ready.</h2><p class=\"mt-5 text-base leading-7 text-[color:var(--muted-foreground)] sm:text-lg\">The room stays in lobby mode until the host begins the session, then players arrive from the database in randomized room order.</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row\"><div class=\"inline-flex\" tabindex=\"0\"><a class=\"group/button relative inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 overflow-hidden whitespace-nowrap rounded-full border font-semibold tracking-[0.02em] transition-[transform,box-shadow,background-color,border-color,color] duration-200 ease-out will-change-transform disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-[color:var(--ring)] focus-visible:ring-offset-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-[color:var(--background)] border-white/20 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(250,250,250,1),rgba(228,228,231,0.97))] !text-black [&amp;&gt;svg]:!text-black shadow-[inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.62),0_16px_38px_rgba(0,0,0,0.28)] hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-white/24 hover:!text-black hover:[&amp;&gt;svg]:!text-black hover:shadow-[inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.66),0_20px_44px_rgba(0,0,0,0.34)] h-[3.35rem] px-7 text-base sm:px-8\" href=\"/create-room\">Create room<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-4 w-4 transition-transform duration-200 group-hover/button:translate-x-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div><div class=\"inline-flex\" tabindex=\"0\"><a class=\"group/button relative inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 overflow-hidden whitespace-nowrap rounded-full border font-semibold tracking-[0.02em] transition-[transform,